<%# Privacy Policy Page %>
<div class="container mt-5">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto">
      <h1 class="display-4 text-center mb-5">Privacy Policy</h1>
      
      <div class="content">
        <p class="lead">
          Last updated: <%= Date.current.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %>
        </p>
        
        <h3>1. Information We Collect</h3>
        <p>We collect information you provide directly to us, such as when you create an account, update your profile, or contact us. This may include:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Name, email address, and phone number</li>
          <li>Sports profiles, achievements, and media content</li>
          <li>Communication preferences and account settings</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h3>2. How We Use Your Information</h3>
        <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Provide, maintain, and improve our services</li>
          <li>Connect you with other athletes, coaches, and clubs</li>
          <li>Send you updates and communications about our platform</li>
          <li>Respond to your comments and questions</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h3>3. Information Sharing</h3>
        <p>We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal information to third parties without your consent, except:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>With your explicit permission</li>
          <li>To comply with legal obligations</li>
          <li>To protect our rights and safety</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h3>4. Data Security</h3>
        <p>We implement appropriate security measures to protect your personal information against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction.</p>
        
        <h3>5. Your Rights</h3>
        <p>You have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Access and update your personal information</li>
          <li>Delete your account and associated data</li>
          <li>Opt-out of marketing communications</li>
          <li>Request a copy of your data</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h3>6. Contact Us</h3>
        <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:</p>
        <p>
          Email: <a href="mailto:privacy@linksports.in">privacy@linksports.in</a><br>
          Phone: +91-98765-43210
        </p>
        
        <div class="alert alert-info mt-4">
          <i class="fas fa-info-circle me-2"></i>
          We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
